			<h2>1st of Moonstone, 255, Early Winter</h2>
			<p><a href="images/suc_img/year5_27.png"><img class="right" src="images/suc_img/year5_27.png" /></a>Winter is here. Finally dug out the bottom floor of the dining hall. Now I just have to get all of this stone out of here! I quickly put all of the children to task and designate a dump pile outside in the hallway. </p>
			<p>Many dwarves have been dropping off gifts and trinkets hearing the news of my wife. All have been so kind except for the mayor who left a note to <a href="images/suc_img/year5_28.png"> deliver a pewter chest to his quarters</a>, immediately.</p>
